the under side of the world
a rough time getting to the top , the sides was so steep and the bushes so thick
thick as my little finger with some monstrous hooks on it
something laying on the floor in the far corner that looked like a man
the canoe hid in a good place , and had all the traps in the cavern
Daytimes we paddled all over the island in the canoe
a boy 's old speckled straw hat on the floor
the trees off a little ways
a bottle that had had milk in it
